  <div class="restaurant">
    <h2 class="title">Mellisse</h2> 
    <p class="content"> Mellisse restrauant located in Santa Monica, is a fine dining establishment that has been recognized for its outstanding culinary excellence, holding two Michelin stars. This prestigious rating is a testament to the restaurant’s exceptional cooking and high-quality dining experience. Mélisse is known for its intimate setting, offering a unique and personal dining adventure where chefs and sommeliers guide guests through a symphony of 18 servings, featuring the finest ingredients sourced from California farmers across the region. The restaurant prides itself on marrying global flavors with classic and contemporary techniques, ensuring a memorable gastronomic journey for all its patrons.</p >
    
